<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.6.1">
<l>kaimmāṉa maḻakaḷiṟṟaik kaṭalkiṭanta karumaṇiyai</l>
<l>maimmāṉa marakatattai maṟaiyuraitta tirumālai</l>
<l>yemmāṉai yeṉakkeṉṟu miṉiyāṉaip paṉikātta</l>
<l>vammāṉai yāṉkaṇṭa taṇinīrtteṉ ṉaraṅkattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My beholding of the young elephant with a hand-like [trunk],</l>
<l rend="indent">the dark jewel who sleeps in the sea,</l>
<l>The ink-like emerald, Tirumāl who proclaimed the Vedas,</l>
<l>Our lord, the one who is always sweetness to me,</l>
<l>The lord who blocked the rains, was in Araṅkam of the South by lovely waters.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
